      • extract

        public static void extract(AbstractStoryRepresentation asr,
                           ConceptParser cp,
                           edu.stanford.nlp.trees.TypedDependency td,
                           StorySentence storySentence,
                           java.lang.String tdDepId,
                           java.lang.String tdGovId,
                           java.util.List<edu.stanford.nlp.trees.TypedDependency> listDependencies)
        Processes the “nmod” (that is not “nmod:poss” or “nmod:of” or “nmod:tmod” or “nmod:for” or “nmod:with”) TypedDependency relation, for “AtLocation” assertion of nouns.
        Parameters:
        asr - Used to retrieve and store information.
        cp - Used to construct strings to be used as concepts.
        td - Dependency relation from the CoreNLP tool dependency parsing
        storySentence - Story sentence object to store or retrieve the extracted relations
        tdDepId - Position id of the dependency
        tdGovId - Position id of the governor
        listDependencies - List of dependencies parsed by the CoreNLP tool.
